A '''cameo role''' or '''cameo appearance''' (often shortened to just '''cameo''') is a brief appearance of a known person in a work of the [[performing arts]], such as [[Play (theatre)|plays]], [[movie]]s, [[video game]]s and [[television]]. Such a role does not have to be an actor: short appearances by [[movie director]]s, [[politician]]s, [[sportsperson|athletes]], and other [[Celebrity|celebrities]] are common.


